description: Introducing the Palm® Pixi™ Artist Series. Customize your Palm Pixi phone with a limited-edition back cover designed by some of today's most unique and compelling artists. Commissioned exclusively for Palm Pixi, each work is numbered and compatible with Palm Touchstone™ Technology.  Now you can match your back cover with the wallpaper on your phone with this easy to use application!  Read more about the back covers at: http://www.palm.com/artistseries
